    {
      "id": "l3-ttl",
      "title": "Level 3: TTL",
      "prompt": "Add time-to-live. All earlier operations keep working.\n\n**New operation**\n\n- `[\"SET_AT\", timestamp, key, field, value, ttl]` — set `store[key][field]` to `value` with an absolute expiration at `timestamp + ttl` (`ttl` is a positive integer string). Return `\"true\"`.\n\nA field is **expired** when the current query's timestamp is greater than or equal to its absolute expiration time. Expired fields are invisible to `GET`/`SCAN`/`SCAN_BY_PREFIX` (those return `\"\"` for them or skip them during a scan) and `DELETE` returns `\"false\"` for them (they are treated as already gone). A plain `SET` cancels any prior TTL on that field; a new `SET_AT` replaces both the value and the expiration.",
      "signature": {
        "name": "solution",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "queries",
            "type": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ],
        "output": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "tests": [
        {
          "name": "l3-set-at-then-get-before-expiry",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "5",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "alice"
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-get-after-expiry",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "15",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            ""
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-get-at-boundary-is-expired",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice",
                "10"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "11",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            ""
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-set-cancels-ttl",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SET",
                "2",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "bob"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "20",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "bob"
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-scan-excludes-expired",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice"
              ],
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "2",
                "user:1",
                "session",
                "abc",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SCAN",
                "20",
                "user:1"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "name=alice"
          ],
          "visibility": "hidden"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-delete-of-expired-is-false",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "session",
                "abc",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "DELETE",
                "20",
                "user:1",
                "session"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "false"
          ],
          "visibility": "hidden"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-prefix-scan-excludes-expired",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "session_old",
                "x",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SET",
                "2",
                "user:1",
                "session_new",
                "y"
              ],
              [
                "SCAN_BY_PREFIX",
                "20",
                "user:1",
                "session"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "session_new=y"
          ],
          "visibility": "hidden"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-set-at-overrides-prior-expiration",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "2",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "bob",
                "100"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "50",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            "bob"
          ],
          "visibility": "hidden"
        },
        {
          "name": "l3-scan-all-fields-expired-returns-empty",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "a",
                "1",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "2",
                "user:1",
                "b",
                "2",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "SCAN",
                "20",
                "user:1"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "true",
            ""
          ],
          "visibility": "hidden"
        }
      ],
      "languages": {
