    {
      "id": "l4-backup-restore",
      "title": "Level 4: Backup & restore",
      "prompt": "Add time-aware snapshots. All earlier operations keep working.\n\n**New operations**\n\n- `[\"BACKUP\", timestamp]` — snapshot the current state, capturing every **currently live** field's value AND its absolute expiration (where one exists). Return the new backup id as `\"backup{N}\"` where `N` starts at 1 and increments per backup.\n- `[\"RESTORE\", timestamp, backup_id]` — replace the entire state with the snapshot. Backup fields with an absolute expiration **at or before** the restore timestamp are dropped immediately; surviving expiring fields keep their original absolute expiration. Return `\"true\"` on success, or `\"false\"` if the backup id is unknown.",
      "signature": {
        "name": "solution",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "queries",
            "type": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ],
        "output": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "tests": [
        {
          "name": "l4-backup-then-restore",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice"
              ],
              [
                "BACKUP",
                "2"
              ],
              [
                "SET",
                "3",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "bob"
              ],
              [
                "RESTORE",
                "4",
                "backup1"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "5",
                "user:1",
                "name"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "backup1",
            "true",
            "true",
            "alice"
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l4-restore-missing-backup",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "RESTORE",
                "1",
                "ghost"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "false"
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l4-backup-skips-expired",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET_AT",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "session",
                "x",
                "5"
              ],
              [
                "BACKUP",
                "20"
              ],
              [
                "RESTORE",
                "21",
                "backup1"
              ],
              [
                "GET",
                "22",
                "user:1",
                "session"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "expected": [
            "true",
            "backup1",
            "true",
            ""
          ],
          "visibility": "visible"
        },
        {
          "name": "l4-restore-clears-newer-state",
          "args": [
            [
              [
                "SET",
                "1",
                "user:1",
                "name",
                "alice"
              ],
              [
                "BACKUP",
                "2"
              ],
              [
                "SET",
                "3",
                "user:2",
                "name",
                "carol"
              ],
              [
                "RESTORE",
                "4",
                "backup1"
              ],
